# Icon Usage in Nimiq Developer Center

The project prioritizes **Nimiq brand icons** first, then falls back to **Tabler icons** when specific icons aren't available in the Nimiq set.

> **Related Rules**: Icons integrate with [UnoCSS conventions](mdc:.cursor/rules/unocss-usage.mdc), [Nimiq theme components](mdc:.cursor/rules/nimiq-vitepress-theme.mdc), and [documentation authoring](mdc:.cursor/rules/documentation-authoring.mdc) for visual hierarchy.

